# Import templates — adopt EXISTING stateful resources into this Terraform state
# without destroy+recreate / data loss. Use when moving an owned pod (e.g.
# Luminary) onto infra_version 1.8, or re-homing after the naming reset.
#
# HOW TO USE
#   1. Copy the blocks you need into a real `imports.tf` (this .example file is
#      ignored by Terraform).
#   2. Fill each `id` with the existing resource's physical id/name/ARN.
#   3. Set var.pod_name / var.environment so the module's cv-gw-{env}-{pod_name}-*
#      names MATCH the physical names you are importing — otherwise the plan will
#      show a rename (= replace), not a clean adoption.
#   4. `terraform plan` — every imported resource must show "will be imported"
#      then NO destroy (benign tag/config updates are fine).
#   5. `terraform apply`, then DELETE the import blocks (they are one-shot).
#
# DO NOT import random_id.pod_id / random_password.* — they read back wrong and
# plan as replace, breaking pod identity. Instead PRE-SEED the credentials secret
# (GATEWAY_POD_ID / GATEWAY_HMAC_SECRET) before first apply so ignore_changes
# preserves it. See docs + dedicated-gateway-tf-maintenance.md.
#
# Note: the VPC does NOT need an import — to reuse an existing network, set the
# vpc_id / public_subnet_ids / private_subnet_ids variables instead (BYO network).

# --- DynamoDB data table (preserves all chat data) ---
# import {
#   to = module.gateway.aws_dynamodb_table.data
#   id = "cv-gw-prod-luminary-data"
# }

# --- S3 payload bucket (preserves all request/response payloads) ---
# import {
#   to = module.gateway.aws_s3_bucket.payload
#   id = "cv-gw-prod-luminary-payloads-123456789012"
# }

# --- Pod credentials secret (preserves pod identity: GATEWAY_POD_ID/HMAC) ---
# import {
#   to = module.gateway.aws_secretsmanager_secret.pod
#   id = "arn:aws:secretsmanager:us-east-1:123456789012:secret:cv-gw-prod-luminary-credentials-AbCdEf"
# }

# --- Registration secret ---
# import {
#   to = module.gateway.aws_secretsmanager_secret.registration
#   id = "arn:aws:secretsmanager:us-east-1:123456789012:secret:cv-gw-prod-luminary-registration-AbCdEf"
# }
